Igishanga ni agace kubutaka karangwa n'ubushyuhe, acide ndetse n'uburumbuke buke bw'ubutaka  n'amazi asohoka.<ref>https://rw.worldlifeadvice.com/10826632-why-it-is-necessary-to-protect-the-swamps</ref> igishanga ni ahantu hari ubutaka butose, akenshi bufite amazi, ibiti n'ibindi bimera bitandukanye.<ref>https://www.collinsdictionary.com/dictionary/english/swamp</ref>

== Ibishanga mu Rwanda ==
Ibishanga bibarirwa mu mitungo y'amazi leta ifite, ibishanga bihoramo amazi bikaba binakungahaye ku bimera bigomba kurindwa by'umwihariko, ibishanga bigomba kwitabwaho hitawe cyane kuruhare n'umumaro bigira mu kubungabunga urusobe rw'ibinyabuzima.<ref>https://menyanibi.rw/menya-itegeko-rigenga-ibidukikije-mu-rwanda-2/</ref>

== kurinda ibishanga hitawe no kuburenganzira bw'abaturage ==
kuri uyu munsi isi ihangayikishijwe n'umuvuduko ukomeye wizimira ry'ibishanga. muriki kinyejana kimwe cya kabiri cyabo bimaze kuzimira.<ref>http://isangostar.rw/amakuru/mu-rwanda/article/ukwiyongera-kwabaturage-ku-isonga</ref>

